    "title": "京东开放平台个人/个体店营养保健和传统滋补品类销售激励政策（2026.3.1-2026.6.30）",
    "followRuleId": "1346676341082533888",
    "content": "<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">为鼓励商家在京东开放平台积极经营营养保健和传统滋补类目，特制定激励政策，符合条件商家可获得最长4个月平台运营支持服务费100%返还激励，激励以现金形式返还，进一步降低商家经营成本，助力老商家层级跃迁，具体内容如下：</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一、参与商家</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">限京东开放平台商品经营类目为营养保健和传统滋补的个人/个体店铺，仅限2026年2月28日及之前完成入驻的店铺，店铺ID需归属于京喜事业部下，具体归属关系可咨询对接店铺/类目运营，结果以店铺/类目运营反馈为准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">指定类目</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一级类目：营养保健、传统滋补；</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二、激励政策</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、激励周期：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2026</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年3月1日至2026年6月30日（以下称为&ldquo;考核期&rdquo;）</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">数据同比期：2025年3月1日至2025年6月30日</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、激励规则：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2026</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年激励模式及返还模式，具体如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（1）激励模式：以传统滋补+营养保健类目合计销售 GMV（计算方式详见3、数据口径）为基础进行考核。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（2）返还模式：按月度考核，并按月度整体达标档位发放。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（3）返还形式：考核达标后，次月以现金形式返还至京麦钱包。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（4）激励金额：激励周期内激励类目产生实付扣点*激励比例</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、数据口径：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（1）销售 GMV口径：为Net GMV（实收销售额），即考核期内店铺内该类目下单，且在2026年6月30日之前完成的订单产生的GMV【须剔除退货、未确认收货，取消订单、虚拟商品订单，刷单等风控订单、使用优惠券金额的订单等】，考核周期结束后，次月进行数据计算。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、政策详情</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（1）已享受平台特殊费率的订单所产生的GMV均计入本政策内进行达量考核，但不再给予本政策下返利。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">0.6%</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">交易服务费另行单独收取，GMV单位：人民币元</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 126.75pt; background: #BE1A1D; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"169\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">考核类目</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 105.0pt; background: #BE1A1D; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"140\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">店铺类型</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 96.0pt; background: #BE1A1D; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"128\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">激励政策类型</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84.0pt; background: #BE1A1D; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"112\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">单月销售额</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 105.75pt; background: #BE1A1D; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"141\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">增长要求</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 125.25pt; background: #BE1A1D; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"167\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">销售金额考核/返还口径</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 119.25pt; background: #BE1A1D; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"159\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">返利形式</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100.5pt; background: #BE1A1D; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"134\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">考核/返利基础</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 78.75pt; background: #BE1A1D; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"105\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">标准扣点</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 139.5pt; background: #BE1A1D; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"186\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">返还扣点</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 96.0pt; background: #BE1A1D; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"128\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">返还方式</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 126.75pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"169\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">营养保健/传统滋补</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 105.0pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"140\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">个人/个体店</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 96.0pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"128\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">销售激励</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84.0pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"112\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">150</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">万</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 105.75pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"141\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">同比增长20%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 125.25pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"167\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">销售GMV</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 119.25pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"159\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">阶梯返利</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100.5pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"134\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">类目</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 78.75pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"105\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.5%/5%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 139.5pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"186\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">返技术服务费的100%</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 96.0pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"128\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">现金</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 126.75pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"169\">\n<p style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">营养保健/传统滋补</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 105.0pt; background: white; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"140\">\n<p 